	<text>
		<body>
			<p>Alla Columbia University?, New York</p>
			<p>[Torino,] 16 luglio 1930</p>
			<p>Dear Mr Director,</p>
			<p>here is the form you asked for.</p>
			<p>I hope you find it satisfactory and clear and kindly pray you of a fast reply, as I must decide in this month.</p>
			<p>Very truly yours</p>
			<p>Cesare Pavese</p>
			<p>P.S. I beg your pardon, but last time you mistook my address: it is not Corino, but Torino.</p>
		</body>
